2026-04-15T23:20:00.2123551Z       "body": "When tracebacks are formatted with Rich, code lines are currently truncated to 88 characters (or less if terminal width is less).\r\n\r\nThis PR:\r\n* Makes it display full line if terminal width is large enough\r\n* Allows configuring it to wrap text instead of truncating it if terminal width is small\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Small terminal width (before - after):**\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"695\" height=\"263\" alt=\"Screenshot from 2026-04-16 01-06-26\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/539a9f1d-958c-4796-ad07-b0fabef2fef9\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=\"695\" height=\"281\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c63cc8b9-c0f1-4fbe-9fa8-9fe274aaf2bd\" />\r\n\r\n**After is with `pretty_exceptions_word_wrap=True`**\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Wide terminal (before - after):**\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1105\" height=\"237\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c0ec385c-d9f7-4dd6-b4cf-dd133863977f\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1105\" height=\"237\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/73972bbd-56d2-4598-b733-aa88d395c027\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nIf the idea is accepted, I will need to add test",
